<tr id="L128"><td><a href="#L128">128</a></td><td>ARCHER:  Those people weren't rebels, and I wasn't trying to start a rebellion. I am not your enemy!</td></tr>

<tr id="L129"><td><a href="#L129">129</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: He gets punished by pain sticks.</td></tr>

<tr id="L130"><td><a href="#L130">130</a></td><td>MAGISTRATE:  This tribunal is in recess.</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Prison cell</td></tr>
<tr id="L131"><td><a href="#L131">131</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Archer tries a bit of the meat on the bone, but spits it out. Kolos enters.</td></tr>

