<tr id="L322"><td><a href="#L322">322</a></td><td>KOLOS:  The sentence is death. You condemn this man to Rura Pente. What is the life expectancy of a prisoner there? Six months, a year at the most? And you expect us to believe that this is an act of mercy.</td></tr>

